Usually, once I drop him right at the feet on the MT, we have the ST attack at the same time. Thus creating the first two people on said mobs hate list. It's worked everytime. Let the MT gain agro for 10 seconds, and he'll call people in. If MT goes down, everyone stops for 10 seconds so ST builds agro, and the person on rampage calls out he has rampage agro.<br>
